## Errors & Mistakes
- First shim attempt was a bare star re-export; test_base_object_classes
  failed: star-import honors __all__, and test_only_example.__all__ EXCLUDES
  TestOnlyNestedBaseModel which tests import. Hardened every shim (including
  PR3's leaf shims) with a PEP 562 __getattr__ forwarding to the impl module.
- 7 llm_structured_completion_model tests failed after the move because they
  @patch'd get_weave_client on the OLD module path — patching a shim's
  attribute does not affect the implementation module's globals. Updated the
  patch targets. THIS IS THE CANONICAL SHIM GOTCHA: mock.patch targets must
  name the module where the function is LOOKED UP, and shims are not that
  module.

